_:N1da803d53b294b57aa755290bc77a9cf <http://schema.org/text> "We are Cyber & Specialist Operations Command’s innovation team, connecting world-class technology and talent with users across Defence. " .
_:N1da803d53b294b57aa755290bc77a9cf <http://schema.org/datePublished> "2018-02-28T13:52:25+00:00"^^<http://schema.org/Date> .
