<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations> <http://schema.org/name> "Organisations" .
_:N1da803d53b294b57aa755290bc77a9cf <http://schema.org/image> <https://www.gov.uk/assets/frontend/govuk_publishing_components/govuk-schema-placeholder-16x9-30e6c0e035636ee6b9dc72ae254bcd4a925182805afe7c5b7170cf2394894b28.png> .
